replies.body:
I have the same issue! I was about to post something about this. Sometimes I am able to have the screen load up, but the other day when I tried to craft my 10 key fragments into keys, it would show the crafting animation, and then get stuck there. At the same time I would the get status message "You have been disconnected from PvP.net". After many tries and not trying to rush through the key animation and letting the whole animation run, I was able to forge my keys. However I am still getting client disconnection problems whenever I access Hextech Crafting and try to do something with it. Also when I try to restart client, on first or second login tries I can't login, I have to restart the client multiple times to log in successfully after getting dc'd from Hextech Crafting.

Also when Hextech Crafting first came out, everything was fine, it was only until more recently it started acting up.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
